----- EMAIL 2026-06-12T08:49:49.501479 -----
To: manager@bank.lk
Subject: New Circular 65/2025: Human Resource Poticy on Remote Wcrk

Dear Compliance Manager,

A new circular has been published.

Summary:
Remote Work Agreement: A written Agreement entered into by and between the Employee/ Remote Worker and the Employer / Management of the Bank. Approved Remote Work Location (RWL): A place where employees will be authorized to carry out their official duties away from the Primary Work Location, subject to approval of the Management. Remote Worker shall be required to set up / designate a workspace rry,ithin the remote work lo Eation for placement and installation of equipment.

Please acknowledge by 19 Jun 2026.

